title: Icestudio - Open source GUI for FPGA design and programming, visual drag-and-drop, no code required!

media:group.media:title: Icestudio - Open source GUI for FPGA design and programming, visual drag-and-drop, no code required!
media:group.media:description:
Here I demonstrate the icestudio tools: an open source GUI-based FPGA design and synthesys tool. Drag-and-drop to create your design visually in a GUI! No need to write any code. Icestudio is fun to work with and easy to get going on your own Go Board. No code is required to work with this tool!

Support me on Patreon: http://patreon.com/nandland
Try icestudio: http://icestudio.io
Buy a Go Board: https://www.nandland.com/goboard/introduction.html
